        "name": "LMT MRGG-A 7.62x51mm Marksman Rifle",
        "shortName": "MRGG-A",
        "description": "LMT's 7.62x51 gas gun built on the company's signature monolithic upper platform. The Modular Rail Gas Gun pairs a one-piece upper and rail for a rock-solid optic-to-bore relationship with an ambidextrous lower and two-stage trigger, delivering the reach and terminal authority of full-power .308 in a semi-automatic package that still handles like a fighting rifle. Purpose-built for designated-marksman and precision duty roles."
      }
